| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0251 — Recovery Inhibition (fog)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2504a37a-9c6b-5bd1-9e39-4b4e2713f26e"
